## 8. Risk register

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| TS 7 native preview (`tsgo`) is alpha | Pin to specific version, document fallback to `tsc` |
| Bun + Next.js patterns don't 1:1 map | hono router (not Next pages), keep React only for client islands |
| 1421 TS files need audit for `next/*` imports | Add lint rule `no-restricted-imports` for `next/*`, fix per-file |
| Bifrost version churn | Pin, vendor locally if needed |
| Existing 8 sprint WTs blocked on old stack | Cherry-pick WIP onto step-2 branch, don't block step-1 |

## 9. Definition of done (step-1)

- [ ] `bun install` succeeds
- [ ] `bun run typecheck` (tsgo) passes with 0 errors
- [ ] `bun test` passes
- [ ] `bun run build` produces dist
- [ ] `bun run start` serves `/health` returning 200
- [ ] Bifrost provider registry loads, all 16+ providers enumerate
- [ ] Old `next.config.js` / `app/` / `pages/` deleted
- [ ] `pyproject.toml` + `.python-version` committed, uv-managed
- [ ] PR opened with green CI

